title: NFL Trade Deadline Preview, Buyers/Sellers (Football 10/28)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Jason La Canfora to preview Tuesday's NFL Trade Deadline. Will and JLC discuss the Redskins and Bengals refusal to make deals (1:30), the most aggressive buyers (12:10) and names that might be on new teams pretty soon.
